flowchart TD
    C((C)) --> Load[Load Leaflet map of San Joaquin<br/>pins color-coded by sitio]
    Load --> Act{Action?}

    Act -- Click existing pin --> Pop[Popup: residents living there<br/>+ PWD / Senior / Solo flags]
    Pop --> PE{Edit or remove?}
    PE -- Edit --> Upd[Update household] --> SaveU[Save to Supabase]
    PE -- Remove --> Del[Delete household] --> SaveU

    Act -- Click empty map --> Drop[Drop temporary pin]
    Drop --> PickHead[Select household head<br/>shows their existing HH No.]
    PickHead --> FillHH[Fill address & housing type]
    FillHH --> Has{Head already<br/>has a household?}
    Has -- Yes --> UpdLoc[UPDATE that household's location]
    Has -- No --> Ins[INSERT new household]
    UpdLoc --> SaveU
    Ins --> SaveU

    Act -- Pinned list --> Fly[Fly map to selected household]

    SaveU --> Refresh[Refresh map] --> R((R))
    Fly --> R
